{
  "stem": "7506.5",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Although we never got any news in the camp, we always surmised things were bad for the Germans because of their behavior towards us.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "The worse they were, the worse we thought was their military campaign.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And we'd see these trails of aircraft.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I mean hundreds, literally hundreds, in daylight.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Hundreds of these trials of aircraft, you know, the vapor of trails.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And one time I remember distinctly there was a dogfight above the camp, and a few people got hit in the camp.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And I remember some of the barracks were shot up.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A dogfight, that's between opposing aircraft, you know, trying to shoot each other down.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it became such a low-level dogfight that it impacted the camp with stray bullets.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I believe some adults did get hit.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we knew by that time things were going against the Germans.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we started to feel maybe, as children-- and mostly I say to you the ones that were well were still playing-- we thought maybe we would get out.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Maybe something would happen.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We would get out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We could go home.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Some of the children's health started to deteriorate, because by that time, our nutrition was a lot worse than what it had been.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Although we were getting from Luba food, we suffered more nutritionally.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The weaker children, I think, got weak.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then, of course, we got lice.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And from the lice, you get typhus.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I personally had typhus.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I think most of the children had typhus.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We still had all our own clothes, the original clothes.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I still had that coat that I'd brought from England with my grandmother in 1939 to Holland.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I still had my old ski boots.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "My sister got ill.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "My sister couldn't eat hardly anything anymore.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
